title: Creedence Clearwater Revival - Live In Europe [320k MP3]
description:
Live in Europe is a first live album by American band Creedence Clearwater Revival, released in 1973 documenting the Mardi Gras tour. The album is notable because it is was performed as a trio following Tom Fogerty's departure. The record was released despite John Fogerty's strong objections.
